cu.explanation_en: Changed GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF from "192.168.70.132" to "10.0.0.1" to simulate unreachable routing definitions, causing IP range conflict and CU inability to reach AMF.

du.explanation_en: Changed local_n_address from "127.0.0.3" to "10.0.0.3" to simulate unreachable routing definitions, causing IP range conflict and DU inability to reach CU.
du.explanation_zh: 将 local_n_address 从 "127.0.0.3" 更改为 "10.0.0.3" 以模拟不可达的路由定义，导致 IP 范围冲突和 DU 无法到达 CU。
